{"tid":848271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"巴絲有冇試過覺得空虛,覺得冷","createTime":"2018-10-04T19:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T09:16:51.000Z","uid":140357,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c5a0327824198a093855a47001c4ba4e2c6118","tid":848271,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T19:58:39.000Z","msg":"我試過,夜晚落街去打波,行行下突然一陣冷風吹過,個心揪住揪住咁。然後諗起自己24歲仲A0,夜晚只可以一個人打波,而個個朋友就同女友一齊行街,令我諗起羅文果首幾許風雨。。。<br />\n---------------<br />\n一生之中誰沒痛苦 得失少不免<br />\n看透世態每種風雨 披身打我面<br />\n身處高峰 嚐盡雨絲 輕風的加冕<br />\n<br />\n偶爾踫上了急風 步伐未凌亂<br />\n心底之中知分寸 得失差一線<br />\n披荊斬棘的挑戰 光輝不眷戀<br />\n-----------<br />\n最後我雖然冇女友,但都想happy share我嘅理想女友比大家。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/035817_5b5af53fc7057114d7bb81aaba1c66f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F035817_5b5af53fc7057114d7bb81aaba1c66f9.jpg&h=c2ea43b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/035819_0dc416c605998836cc1eb743149c00f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F035819_0dc416c605998836cc1eb743149c00f0.jpg&h=1234c797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/035821_f557e07838c309ae0cee1290447f698c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F035821_f557e07838c309ae0cee1290447f698c.jpg&h=9b12577f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/035823_2234a76fdc0534f1257e11b092690606.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2F035823_2234a76fdc0534f1257e11b092690606.jpg&h=0bad8e76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/05/035825_73e81f3c0176ff27aef0ff5674897fa3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http